{"title":"竹号（二首）","authors":["傅仇"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹号（二首）\t傅仇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜闻竹号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原还没睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员在吹竹号；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像火在燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像雷在奔跑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是报新竹成林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫荡了雪霰风暴？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是报腊梅花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击退了残冬寒潮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是庆公社丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五谷丰登畜满槽？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是庆春满茅屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新人新事添千条？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是迎接新的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天里就奏出迎春调？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是迎接新的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头一年就吹响进军号？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声响彻平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破冬夜雾罩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那竿竿翠竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成排排竹号！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像火在燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像雷在奔跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声抬着平原飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原兴奋得睡不着觉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬　夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好暖和的茅屋呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正围在一堆讨论计划。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队的庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全盘摆在油灯下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年的庄稼呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样才能多结果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多开花？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这场生产仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又该怎么打？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地就听你一句话！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅屋外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任那北风呼呼刮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅屋内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堆大火似红霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着社员们摇动大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着社员们指挥兵马！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季风云任驾驭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风春雨遍地洒："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催小麦快快发芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催油菜快快开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催拖拉机破开冻土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催河水冲出堤闸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响着春天的步伐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大丰收的根子已扎下！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}